  ColorLander
  ***********

   A lander clone mixed with memory and transport concept.
   
   memory:
   You are given a longer sequence of colors
   when you complete the one you have been given before.   
   -Can you navigate your ship
   while remembering the sequence?

    Controls:
   
     arrow keys to thrust.

   
   This game loads maps from data/colorlander/
   and they are fully editable.
   the iff bitmaps can have any width and height.

   A color 2(white) pixel places the player there like this:
 
                    ooo
                   ooooo
                  ooo ooo 
   white pixel--> wo   oo
  
 
   Send me cool maps, and you receive a full version of watchNplay! 



